<p class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle"><b><u>New York Times</u>: &#8220;Virtually Every Trump Speech Includes A Reference To One Of His Hotels Or Casinos&#8221; And Sales Of His 1987 Book Skyrocketed After He Repeatedly Touted It On The Trail.</b> &#8220;Virtually every Trump speech
