<p class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle"><b>Trump Once Held A Campaign Press Conference, Then Led The National Media On A Tour Of His New Hotel.</b> &#8220;It was billed as a campaign event, but all Donald Trump wanted to do was show off his fancy new property. Trump led a
